{"tid":1492243,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"愛國老坑劉德華：蔡英文在挑戰國家的底線，是不可饒恕的！","createTime":"2019-08-20T17:47:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T18:56:23.000Z","uid":34047,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7ff820dd9f6c158b98b3e5fca23703996da37db1","tid":1492243,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:47:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/498565150232596/posts/2457158951039863/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F498565150232596%2Fposts%2F2457158951039863%2F&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41C1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=ef578494\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/498565150232596/posts/2457158951039863/</a><br />\n<br />\n自6月反修例風波開始，台灣領導人蔡英文為鞏固自己的政治生涯，爭取連任，不惜頻頻發表港獨言論，煽動港獨分子搞事，企圖分裂及挑戰中國及一國兩制底線。此事，引起中國強烈不滿，決定拒絕參加原定於今年11月，在台北舉行的金馬獎頒獎典禮，隨即愛國藝人劉德華也帶頭宣佈退出金馬獎。劉德華表示，他堅決與分裂國家主權的行為相抗衡，因為這種行為就是在挑戰國家的底線，是不可饒恕的。華仔言出必行做得好，支持華仔即LIKE！<br />\n<br />\n👇 記得Follow 我哋 👇 <br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://instagram.com/silentmajority.hk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fsilentmajority.hk%2F&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41C1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=29163e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">instagram.com/silentmajority.hk/</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://fb.com/silentmajorityhk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fsilentmajorityhk&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41C1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=4ee7ae72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.com/silentmajorityhk</a><br />\nWeibo: <a href=\"https://weibo.com/u/6655322587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2Fu%2F6655322587&d=DXuv2gayA%2Byyjyt3RGK41C1yjuEIKew%2F2lwpseS6mRM%3D&h=7de88dcb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://weibo.com/u/6655322587</a><br />\n#幫港出聲 #劉德華 #蔡英文 #金馬獎 #掃毒2"},{"pid":"6a8ef8e9e2343fad2e049f696f79cab1177bde71","tid":1492243,"uid":57542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T17:50:18.000Z","msg